Description: The Flight into Egypt; the Virgin and the Christ Child on donkey, led by Joseph; small plate; later state with retouchings; fifth state with Watelet's signature removed; copy in reverse after Rembrandt Etching
Producer name: Print made by: Claude Henri Watelet (re-work)
Print made by: François Basan (workshop re-work)
Curator's comments: For an earlier state of this plate and comment see S.6108. For the original etching by Rembrandt and comment see F,4.100.

Hind 1923 / A Catalogue of Rembrandt's Etchings; chronologically arranged and completely illustrated (105) (copy undescribed)
